text: Cornulariidae is a family of soft corals in the suborder Stolonifera. ==Genera== The World Register of Marine Species includes the following two genera in the family: *Cervera Lopez-Gonzalez, Ocana, Garcia-Gomez & Nunez, 1995 *Cornularia Lamarck, 1816 ==References== Category:Alcyonacea Category:Cnidarian families
title: Cornulariidae
